node.text: For #HispanicHeritageMonth, @daniel_fuentes72 shares his #TunedByCultura story of how his Hispanic culture melds with his passion for the import car community. Daniel inherited his love for cars from his grandfather and father. His ‘96 Honda Civic is the true representation of his Hispanic culture. “When I built my car, I had so much help from other Hispanics and the Honda car community."
